name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Randolph BARKSDALE, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 28th day of April, 2009, the “Petition for Permission to File a Petition for Reconsideration from Denial of Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc,” which is treated as an Application for Relief, is DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
